 with dried fruits are characteristic.", "Spanish cuisine is known for its tapas culture, paella from Valencia, and the use of olive oil, garlic, and cured ham like jam\u00c3\u00b3n ib\u00c3\u00a9rico. Regional diversity spans from seafood in Galicia to stews in Castilla y Le\u00c3\u00b3n.", "Indian cuisine is characterized by its extensive use of spices, lentils, and rice, with regional variations across the subcontinent. Popular dishes include curry, biryani, naan bread, and tandoori preparations.", "Argentinian cuisine is dominated by beef and grilling traditions, with asado barbecue being the national culinary event. Empanadas, chimichurri sauce, and Malbec wine are hallmarks of this South American food culture."], "scores": [0.909690390488774, 0.8677182792082346, 0.8604411894198702, 0.8482732767590728, 0.8376825746145208], "model_name": "gte-small", "document_ids": ["Ethiopian", "Moroccan", "Spanish", "Indian", "Argentinian"]}}